§ 155.160 USE DISTRICTS.
The following zoning districts are divided into either general use or conditional zoning districts:
(A) Regular zoning districts.
(1) R-A or R-A-CD;
(2) R-20 or R-20-CD;
(3) R-12 or R-12-CD;
(4) R-8 or R-8-CD;
(5) R-M or R-M-CD;
(6) H-B or H-B-CD;
(7) N-B or N-B-CD;
(8) C-S or C-S-CD;
(9) S-P or S-P-CD;
(10) G-I or G-I-CD;
(11) H-I or H-I-CD.
(B) Overlay districts.
(1) WS-III-CA;
(2) WS-III-BW or WS-III-BW-CD;
(3) WS-IV-CA;
(4) WS-IV-PA or WS-IV-PA-CD;
(5) QD.
